scenes.name: Turner
scenes.text: Hey, April!

scenes.name: April
scenes.text: Hi, dad!

scenes.name: Turner
scenes.text:
Why do you keep climbing up here? You're too old for
this.

scenes.name: Turner
scenes.text: These silly tricks are for kids.

scenes.name: April
scenes.text:
It's perfectly safe; I've seen you jump down from
here all the time.

scenes.name: Turner
scenes.text: Hey, it takes a lot of practice to do that...

scenes.name: April
scenes.text: Besides, I can see really far from up here!

scenes.name: April
scenes.text:
That guy over there is creeping me out though;
he looks like he's just waiting for something.

scenes.name: Turner
scenes.text: What guy?!?

scenes.name: April
scenes.text: Over there!

scenes.name: Turner
scenes.text: I'll go see what he's up to.

scenes.name: Turner
scenes.text: Hi, Sarah!####

scenes.name: Sarah#####
scenes.text: Hi, honeybunny!

scenes.name: Sarah###
scenes.text:
Our daughter is up on the lookout ruins and refuses
to come down.

scenes.name: Turner
scenes.text: Again?!?

scenes.name: Turner
scenes.text: Ok, I'll get her to come down.

scenes.name: Turner
scenes.text: Hi, Skipper!

scenes.name: Skipper
scenes.text: Hey, Turner!

scenes.name: Skipper
scenes.text: What's all this talk about hiring guards?

scenes.name: Skipper
scenes.text: There's never been any trouble here while I've been incharge!

scenes.name: Turner
scenes.text: The raiders are getting more confident... you neverknow.

scenes.name: Skipper
scenes.text: I've seen you when you get mad; I think you couldtake care of yourself.

scenes.name: Turner
scenes.text: It's not me that I'm worried about.

scenes.name: Turner
scenes.text: Hey, Clover!

scenes.name: Clover
scenes.text: Wha, time to wake up already?

scenes.name: Turner
scenes.text: Why are you so sleepy?

scenes.name: Clover
scenes.text: I had a horrible dream last night...

scenes.name: Clover
scenes.text: I don't want to talk about it.

scenes.name: Turner
scenes.text: Ah, ok.

scenes.name: Turner
scenes.text: Hey, Jack######!

scenes.name: Jack###
scenes.text: Hi, Turner! Could you do me a huge favor?

scenes.name: Turner
scenes.text: Sure, what is it?

scenes.name: Jack###
scenes.text: I went to the Rocky Hall a few days ago and hired twoguards to help protect our village.

scenes.name: Jack###
scenes.text: But they haven't come yet!

scenes.name: Turner
scenes.text: Lazy bastards. I'll check up on them next time I goover there.

scenes.name: Jack###
scenes.text: Thanks!

hotspots.text: Remember that crouching, not running, increases jump height
